            <div class="mt-5 col-12 col-xl-6">
              <div class="features__item">
                <span class="features__icon  features__icon--server"></span>
                <h4 class="font-weight-bold">Large file support</h4>
                <p>In addition to IPFS, Array.IO supports local storage which can be used to store large amounts of data</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-5 col-12 col-xl-6">
              <div class="features__item">
                <span class="features__icon features__icon--key"></span>
                <h4 class="font-weight-bold">High cryptographic strength</h4>
                <p>Array.IO keychain brings together different implementations of the Elliptic Curve cryptography to ensure that any key type is supported and managed in a secure way.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
